@Comment:	Chi eats with Mot , 5 year old Sis , and 2 year old Bro for about 17 minutes. The little boy is fairly disruptive. There is a lot of conversation , but most of it focuses on the children's immediate surroundings rather than on more abstract topics. The children appear to be very active and verbal; there is some competition for Mot's attention. Check out the explicit vocabulary instruction (initiated by Chi) for the word guest.
